snippet.title: Jessica's Cupcake Café - PC Game Trailer
snippet.description: Get ready to conquer the world with cupcakes in this exciting new time-management casual PC game!  A small Brooklyn bakery owned by Jessicas uncle is about to be forced out of business by a large chain of bakeries.  However, being fresh out of college and armed with a passion for baking cupcakes, Jessica offers her uncle a helping hand.  Its up to you to help Jessica build her business and grow her small café into a delicious empire.  Loaded with hundreds of cupcake designs, dozens of kitchen upgrades and over forty levels of baking action, Jessicas Cupcake Café has the ingredients for sweet success.  As an added bonus, the game features a cupcake cookbook filled with recipes for you to make at home!
